import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { useNavigate, Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Container, Typography, Card, CardContent, Button, Select, MenuItem, FormControl, InputLabel, Grid, IconButton, Divider } from '@mui/material'; import { List, ListItem, ListItemText } from '@mui/material'; import MenuIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Menu'; import ExitToAppIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ExitToApp'; import AccountBalanceWalletIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AccountBalanceWallet'; import GroupIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Group'; import GroupAddIcon from '@mui/icons-material/GroupAdd'; import AccountCircleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AccountCircle'; import RuleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Rule'; import HelpOutlineIcon from '@mui/icons-material/HelpOutline'; import SecurityIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Security'; import AssignmentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Assignment'; import FooterMenu from '../Footer.jsx'; import './Team.css'; const Team = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [teamData, setTeamData] = useState({ registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00, cumulativeTeamSize: 0, generations: [ { percentage: 18, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00 }, { percentage: 6, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00 }, { percentage: 3, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00 }, ], }); const [filter, setFilter] = useState('All'); const [menuOpen, setMenuOpen] = useState(false); const handleFilterChange = (event) => setFilter(event.target.value); const handleViewTeamList = () => navigate('/team-list'); const toggleMenu = () => setMenuOpen(!menuOpen); const logout = () => { localStorage.removeItem('authToken'); navigate('/login'); }; return (
